OL,3,CResidents 'devastated' after bus route
OL,4,Caxed
OL,6,FResidents in Gloucestershire have said
OL,7,Fthey are 'furious' after the axing of
OL,8,Ftheir local bus service.
OL,10,FThe 84/85 bus, which connects Wotton-
OL,11,Funder-Edge and villages in South
OL,12,FGloucestershire to Yate, where many
OL,13,Fcatch trains into the city, stopped on
OL,14,F1 September.
OL,16,FAlistair lives in Wotton-under-Edge
OL,17,Fand lost his job after 21 years, after
OL,18,Fno longer being able to get the bus to
OL,19,FYate when the service was axed.
