OL,3,CResidents 'devastated' after bus route
OL,4,Caxed
OL,6,F"I am just totally devastated because
OL,7,Fthere is no way for me to get to Yate,
OL,8,Fand Yate is such a perfect place for
OL,9,Fwork for us."
OL,11,FIsaac is in his second year of college
OL,12,Fand says now the service has ben axed
OL,13,F"I've got no way to get to college".
OL,15,FTeresa is a fruit and veg shop owner
OL,16,Fin the town, and says it's been a
OL,17,F"domino effect".
OL,19,F"People can't get into Wotton and
OL,20,Fwe've lost trade, we're a dying high
OL,21,Fstreet anyway", she said.
