OL,6,FCouncils say services have been
OL,7,Freduced due to lack of demand.
OL,9,FCampaigner, Barbara disagreed, telling
OL,10,FITV News: "That's just not true."
OL,12,F"Our 84/85 bus was well used, post
OL,13,FCovid the numbers were low, as they
OL,14,Fwere everywhere. We built it up, it
OL,15,Fwas more sustainable, it's more well
OL,16,Fused than many services", she said.
