OL,4,Caxed
OL,6,FIn a statement, Gloucestershire County
OL,7,FCouncil said: "The council partially
OL,8,Ffunds a small proportion of this
OL,9,Fservice as only a minimal section of
OL,10,Fthe route lies within our county.
OL,12,F"When we were made aware it was under
OL,13,Fthreat, we worked frequently with WECA
OL,14,Fand South Gloucestershire Council, and
OL,15,Foffered more money in an attempt to
OL,16,Fsecure the route. Sadly, while we
OL,17,Ftried everything to save it this was
OL,18,Fnot the final outcome."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
