OL,4,Caxed
OL,6,FThe cuts were at the centre of a
OL,7,FParliament debate was held on
OL,8,FWednesday 11 September by Glastonbury
OL,9,Fand Somerton Lib Dem MP Sarah Dyke.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the debate she said: "The
OL,12,Flack of funding, sparsity of routes,
OL,13,Fand smaller population centres has
OL,14,Fresulted in one in four bus routes
OL,15,Fceasing to exist in county and rural
OL,16,Fareas over the last 11 years."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
