OL,6,FThe debate was also attended by the
OL,7,FLabour MP for Stroud, Simon Opher who
OL,8,Fhighlighted problems with cross-border
OL,9,Frural buses which require "agreement
OL,10,Ffrom all of the different local
OL,11,Fauthorities to fund it" which "is
OL,12,Fputting a severe strain on rural
OL,13,Fpopulations."
